<p><a name="Books" id="Books"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Digital_signature&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Books">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>J. Katz and Y. Lindell, "Introduction to Modern Cryptography" (Chapman &amp; Hall/CRC Press, 2007)</li>
</ul>
<p>For books in English on electronic signatures, see:</p>
<ul>
<li>Stephen Mason, Electronic Signatures in Law (Tottel, second edition, 2007);</li>
<li>Dennis Campbell, editor, E-Commerce and the Law of Digital Signatures (Oceana Publications, 2005);</li>
<li>Lorna Brazell, Electronic Signatures Law and Regulation, (Sweet &amp; Maxwell, 2004);</li>
<li>M. H. M Schellenkens, Electronic Signatures Authentication Technology from a Legal Perspective, (TMC Asser Press, 2004).</li>
</ul>
<p>For translations of electronic signature cases from Europe, Brazil, China and Colombia into English, see the Digital Evidence and Electronic Signature Law Review</p>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
