ki/GMR_(cryptography)" title="GMR (cryptography)">GMR</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Goldwasser-Micali_cryptosystem" title="Goldwasser-Micali cryptosystem">Goldwasser-Micali</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hidden_Field_Equations" title="Hidden Field Equations">HFE</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Integrated_Encryption_Scheme" title="Integrated Encryption Scheme">IES</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Lamport_signature" title="Lamport signature">Lamport</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/McEliece_cryptosystem" title="McEliece cryptosystem">McEliece</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Merkle-Hellman" title="Merkle-Hellman">Merkle-Hellman</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/MQV" title="MQV">MQV</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Naccache-Stern_cryptosystem" title="Naccache-Stern cryptosystem">Naccache-Stern</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/NTRUEncrypt" title="NTRUEncrypt">NTRUEncrypt</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/NTRUSign" title="NTRUSign">NTRUSign</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Paillier_cryptosystem" title="Paillier cryptosystem">Paillier</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rabin_cryptosystem" title="Rabin cryptosystem">Rabin</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/RSA" title="RSA">RSA</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Okamoto-Uchiyama_cryptosystem" title="Okamoto-Uchiyama cryptosystem">Okamoto-Uchiyama</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Schnorr_signature" title="Schnorr signature">Schnorr</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/SPEKE_(cryptography)" title="SPEKE (cryptogra